summary: This is a fix for having one install of Skyrim and Enderal with MO2.
descriptionHtml:
I came across an issue when running skyrim and enderal with MO2. After playing Enderal, Skyrim had no character voices. After looking through the ini, I found that the sResourceArchiveList2= had things missing for skyrim. I simply added these missing lines to sResourceArchiveList= which fixed the problem for me.
<br /> 
<br />Install
<br />Simply unzip and post into the skyrim Document folder.
<br />This is my first Fix.
author: Servios
